---
import RootLayout from "@/layouts/root-layout.astro";
---

<RootLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy Policy for Clipwise AI Chrome Extension"
>
  <main id="main-content" class="py-12">
    <article class="mx-auto max-w-4xl space-y-8 px-4">
      <header class="space-y-2">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="font-semibold">Clipwise AI</p>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground">
          <time datetime="2026-01-06">Last updated: January 6, 2026</time>
        </p>
      </header>

      <section class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Overview</h2>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground">
          Clipwise AI is a browser extension that converts webpages to Markdown
          format. Your privacy is important to us, and this policy explains how
          the extension handles your data.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Data Collection</h2>
        <p class="font-semibold">
          Clipwise AI does not collect, store, or transmit any personal data or
          webpage content.
        </p>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground">
          All webpage content processing happens entirely within your browser.
          We have no ability to access, view, or store any content you convert.
          The only external communication is for premium license validation (see
          below).
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">How the Extension Works</h2>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground">
          When you click the Clipwise AI extension icon:
        </p>
        <ol class="list-decimal space-y-2 pl-6 text-muted-foreground">
          <li>The extension reads the HTML content of the current webpage</li>
          <li>
            Content is processed locally using Mozilla Readability to extract
            the main article
          </li>
          <li>
            The extracted content is converted to Markdown format using Turndown
          </li>
          <li>
            The result is stored temporarily in your browser's local storage
          </li>
          <li>
            Your daily conversion count is tracked locally to enforce free tier
            limits (resets at midnight)
          </li>
        </ol>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Permissions Explained</h2>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground">
          Clipwise AI requests the following permissions:
        </p>
        <dl class="space-y-4">
          <div>
            <dt class="font-semibold">activeTab</dt>
            <dd class="text-muted-foreground">
              Allows the extension to read the current page's content only when
              you click the extension icon. The extension cannot access any page
              without your explicit action.
            </dd>
          </div>

          <div>
            <dt class="font-semibold">storage</dt>
            <dd class="text-muted-foreground">
              Used to store the converted Markdown, your daily conversion count,
              and premium license data (if applicable) in your browser's local
              storage. All data stays on your device.
            </dd>
          </div>

          <div>
            <dt class="font-semibold">sidePanel</dt>
            <dd class="text-muted-foreground">
              Enables the extension to display the converted Markdown in
              Chrome's built-in side panel interface.
            </dd>
          </div>

          <div>
            <dt class="font-semibold">scripting</dt>
            <dd class="text-muted-foreground">
              Required to inject a small script that reads the page's HTML
              content when you click the extension icon.
            </dd>
          </div>
        </dl>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Premium License Validation</h2>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground">
          If you purchase a premium license, the extension communicates with
          Lemon Squeezy (our payment and licensing provider) to validate your
          license. This is the only external network communication the extension
          makes.
        </p>
        <p class="font-semibold">What data is sent to Lemon Squeezy:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc space-y-2 pl-6 text-muted-foreground">
          <li>Your license key (to verify it's valid and active)</li>
          <li>
            A unique browser instance identifier (to enforce device limitsâ€”up to
            3 browsers per license)
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p class="font-semibold">What is NOT sent:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc space-y-2 pl-6 text-muted-foreground">
          <li>Any webpage content you convert</li>
          <li>Your browsing history or URLs</li>
          <li>Any other personal information</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground">
          License validation occurs when you activate a license and periodically
          (once per day) while using premium features. If you use only the free
          tier, no external network requests are made.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Data Sharing</h2>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground">
          We do not share your webpage content or browsing data with any third
          parties. For premium users, only license validation data (license key
          and browser instance ID) is shared with Lemon Squeezy to verify your
          subscription.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground">
          Clipwise AI integrates with one third-party service:
        </p>
        <dl class="space-y-4">
          <div>
            <dt class="font-semibold">Lemon Squeezy</dt>
            <dd class="text-muted-foreground">
              Our payment and licensing provider. Used only for premium license
              validation. See
              <a
                href="https://www.lemonsqueezy.com/privacy"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="text-primary underline hover:text-primary/80"
                >Lemon Squeezy's Privacy Policy</a
              >
              for their data handling practices.
            </dd>
          </div>
        </dl>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground">
          We do not use any analytics platforms or tracking systems.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Data Security</h2>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground">
          Since all processing occurs locally within your browser and no data is
          transmitted externally, your content remains secure on your device.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground">
          Clipwise AI does not collect any data from any users, including
          children.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground">
          We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Any changes will
          be reflected in the "Last updated" date at the top of this page.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Contact</h2>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground">
          If you have questions about this privacy policy, please contact us at
          <a
            href="mailto:dennismorello@gmail.com"
            class="text-primary underline hover:text-primary/80"
            >dennismorello@gmail.com</a
          >.
        </p>
      </section>

      <aside class="border-t pt-6">
        <p class="text-sm italic text-muted-foreground">
          This privacy policy applies to the Clipwise AI Chrome extension.
        </p>
      </aside>
    </article>
  </main>
</RootLayout>
